<plot>The Lollipop Man (road crossing guard) is an island of safety and control in a thoughtless and dangerous city - a central reservation amidst rushing, chaotic traffic. A little girl and her mother need protection, and he decides to cross the boundaries of duty to save them. Is he a hero - proof positive that one man can change things for the better? Or is he something else entirely?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?340583</url></doc>
